data.description:
Discover your dream home: a 4-bed, 2-bath sanctuary with a captivating great room, seamlessly connecting to a spacious kitchen with a charming breakfast bar. The open floorplan effortlessly flows to the living area and dining room, creating the perfect space for entertaining.

Step into a large backyard with a screened-in lanai, offering a private outdoor retreat. The master bedroom is a luxurious haven with two walk-in closets, a walk-in shower, and a soaking tub. Guest rooms are generously sized, and the guest bathroom features double vanities.

Complete with a 2-car garage, this home is a perfect blend of style and functionality, providing comfort and convenience in every detail. Welcome home!
